@startuml 06-despliegue-objetivo

title Diagrama de Despliegue — Arquitectura Objetivo (post-MVP, escalado horizontal)
header Visión destino: microservicios independientes (Proyecto.md §2, §8.1, §8.2b) — AÚN NO IMPLEMENTADA

!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor LightYellow
  BorderColor Orange
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor LightBlue
  BorderColor Blue
}
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor LightGray
  BorderColor Black
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Gray
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor LightYellow
  BorderColor Orange
}

actor "Jugador" as Jugador

cloud "Vercel / Render Static" as Frontend {
  component "Cliente React + Vite" as Client
}

node "Render Load Balancer\n(o Cloudflare)" as LB

node "Gateway x2-3\n(Render Web Service)" as GWNode {
  component "Express + Socket.io\nAuth middleware, rate limiting,\nenrutamiento, health check" as GW
}

node "Auth Service x1" as AuthNode {
  component "Auth Service\n(solo HTTP)" as Auth
}

package "Servicios horizontales\n(N réplicas cada uno, Render Web Service)" {
  node "Room Service\nxN" as RoomNode {
    component "Room Service" as Room
  }
  node "Game Service\nxN" as GameNode {
    component "Game Service\n(hexagonal)" as Game
  }
  node "Chat Service\nxN" as ChatNode {
    component "Chat Service" as Chat
  }
  node "Bot Service\nxN" as BotNode {
    component "Bot Service" as Bot
  }
}

node "Timer Service\n(1 master + N standby)" as TimerNode {
  component "Timer Service\nleader election" as Timer
}

node "Observability\nx1 (best-effort)" as ObsNode {
  component "Observability Service" as Obs
}

node "Upstash\n(plan pago — HA)" as RedisNode {
  database "Redis\nSentinel / Cluster\n(estado + Pub/Sub)" as Redis
}

Jugador -down-> Client : HTTPS
Client -down-> LB : WSS
LB -down-> GWNode

GWNode -down-> AuthNode : HTTP verify(token)
GWNode -down-> RoomNode : WebSocket
GWNode -down-> GameNode : WebSocket
GWNode -down-> ChatNode : WebSocket
GWNode -down-> Redis : publish(PlayerDisconnected)\n"evento crudo"

RoomNode <-down-> Redis
GameNode <-down-> Redis
ChatNode <-down-> Redis
TimerNode <-down-> Redis : leader election\n(SET NX EX + heartbeat 500ms)
ObsNode -down-> Redis : write KPIs

RoomNode .down.> Redis : publish/consume eventos\n(Pub/Sub)
GameNode .down.> Redis
ChatNode .down.> Redis
BotNode .down.> Redis
TimerNode .down.> Redis
ObsNode .down.> Redis : consume(*)

note bottom of RedisNode
  **Sigue siendo el cuello de botella real** (Proyecto.md §9.6).
  Con plan gratuito: 10K comandos/día. Para 500+ partidas
  concurrentes (~4,000 cmd/s) se necesita plan Enterprise.
end note

note bottom of GWNode
  **SPOF mitigado** con 2+ réplicas + balanceador.
  Sigue siendo el único punto de entrada público
  (principio arquitectónico #5).
end note

note as Costo
  Costo estimado post-MVP: ~$7/mes por servicio adicional
  en Render + ~$15/mes por el plan pago de Upstash
  (Proyecto.md §8.2b). Ya no es $0.
end note

note as Roadmap
  Esta topología es la **meta del roadmap de 2 sprints**
  (Proyecto.md §10), no algo a desplegar ya. El refactor
  hexagonal de Game Service es opcional dentro del Sprint 1;
  la separación física en procesos independientes es post-MVP.
end note

@enduml
